pEL"><span class="nav-number">3.4.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">SpEL</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-1"><a class="nav-link" href="#切面"><span class="nav-number">4.</span> <span class="nav-text">切面</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#术语"><span class="nav-number">4.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">术语</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#创建切面"><span class="nav-number">4.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">创建切面</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#引入新功能"><span class="nav-number">4.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">引入新功能</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></div>
            

